ens of colors defined as not specified nor used in Figma.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Thus the value for these tokens will be “ouds-forbidden-color-value” as returned by the tokenator.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Thus if the token is still used, even if explained in the documentation it should not,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"this special value won’t be successfully parsed as color and the app will crash like expected.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ColorSemanticTokens","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ColorSemanticTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/colorsemantictokens"}}}